gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/mu-hun/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"I found this problem from https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/pull/230853#discussion_r3207728418\n\nOn article pages for four Reach PLC sites[^sites], the aside section contains both recommended articles and ad units. When AdGuard is active, **all article cards in the aside are hidden**, leaving an empty sidebar.\n\n[^sites]: UK news publisher: https://www.reachplc.com/about-us/our-brands\n\n### Affected sites\n- www.birminghammail.co.uk\n- www.mirror.co.uk\n- www.liverpoolecho.co.uk\n- www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk\n\n### Suspected rules\n\nThe aside rules in `BaseFilter/sections/specific.txt` (around [lines 5419–5425](https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/blob/b671a94378b904207a3a9c52e576273b86a00ec0/BaseFilter/sections/specific.txt#L5419-L5425))\nare likely hiding editorial content alongside ad containers:\n\n```adblock\nbirminghammail.co.uk,...##aside span > span.react-loading-skeleton\nbirminghammail.co.uk,...##aside > div[class^=\"sc-\"]:has(> span > span.react-loading-skeleton)\nbirminghammail.co.uk,...##section[data-testid^=\"commercial-\"]\n```\n\n- The `sc-` prefixed styled-components selector with `:has(react-loading-skeleton)`\n- may apply before content hydrates by React, permanently hiding article card containers.\n- The `[data-testid^=\"commercial-\"]` prefix may also match editorial sections.\n\n<details><summary>Screenshots without AdGuard</summary>\n<img  src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/92e09be7-81f6-4579-b474-6ccce156acdc\" />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1767629d-1edf-451c-bcc5-3875021f44ac\" />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2d9dcb4a-193d-43fb-ba4c-7ec58fbe3025\" />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a618fe02-e45f-4319-bd23-5074e85fb553\" />\n</details>\n\n<details><summary>Screenshots with AdGuard active</summary>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3dcba22c-398a-4a0d-bdca-0d7e29ba5e35\" />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6444a62e-9182-4972-b547-952bd2389c6c\" />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c9df861c-c6cd-42ba-9201-55862f4ce29b\" />\n</details>\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nAd units in the aside are hidden. Recommended article cards remain visible.\n\n### Notes\n\nNeed a selector that distinguishes ad-only containers from mixed editorial+ad containers, or a more specific `data-testid` value.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/230858/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/230858/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null,"pinned_comment":null},"label":{"id":762659576,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw3NjI2NTk1NzY=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/labels/A:%20In%20progress","name":"A: In progress","color":"339966","default":false,"description":"Work on the issue is in progress"},"labels":[{"id":252425980,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyNTI0MjU5ODA=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/labels/T:%20Incorrect%20Blocking","name":"T: Incorrect Blocking","color":"ff0000","default":false